leaving nowhere to return♪

264
00:16:13,600 --> 00:16:16,840
♪Borrow the endless cycles♪

265
00:16:17,400 --> 00:16:20,880
♪To fight for the most perfect outcome♪

266
00:16:21,640 --> 00:16:24,000
♪How to trace the threads
and follow cause and effect♪

267
00:16:24,000 --> 00:16:27,760
♪Seeking a strategy without flaw♪

268
00:16:28,040 --> 00:16:32,680
♪How to break free
from this fated yet unforeseen lock♪

269
00:16:32,840 --> 00:16:37,880
♪To live so as to shake the world♪

270
00:16:38,240 --> 00:16:42,360
♪With this journey,
I gain a fiercer edge♪

271
00:16:42,480 --> 00:16:44,560
♪I've planned
before I act countless times♪

272
00:16:44,640 --> 00:16:51,000
♪Fatal danger turned into a jest♪

273
00:16:51,120 --> 00:16:55,320
♪Through this road,
I watch the endless rise and fall♪

274
00:16:55,360 --> 00:16:57,440
♪In the chapters lie ages
of decay and bloom♪

275
00:16:57,440 --> 00:16:59,360
